《'''绝美之城'''》（{{lang-it|'''La grande bellezza'''}}）是一部[[保罗·索伦蒂诺|保罗·索伦蒂诺]]执导的2013年[[意大利电影|意大利电影]]，由意大利与法国公司合制而成。2012年8月9日在[[罗马|罗马]]开拍<ref>{{Cite web|last=De Marco|first=Camillo|date=18 September 2012|url=http://www.cineuropa.org/nw.aspx?t=newsdetail&l=en&did=233533|title=''La grande bellezza'' by Paolo Sorrentino sold in six countries|work=cineuropa.org|publisher=Cineuropa|accessdate=3 March 2013|archive-date=2013-10-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131019140454/http://www.cineuropa.org/nw.aspx?t=newsdetail&l=en&did=233533|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://screenbase.screendaily.com/films/3016-the-great-beauty-la-grande-bellezza|title=The Great Beauty (La Grande Bellezza)|work=Screenbase|publisher=[[Screen_International|Screen International]]|accessdate=3 March 2013|archive-date=2013-10-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131017205550/http://screenbase.screendaily.com/films/3016-the-great-beauty-la-grande-bellezza|dead-url=no}}</ref>，在[[第66届戛纳电影节|第66届戛纳电影节]]主竞赛单元亮相<ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.festival-cannes.fr/en/archives/inCompetition.html | title=Festival de Cannes. Official Selection 2013: In Competition | work=Cannes | accessdate=2 November 2013 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131110201746/http://www.festival-cannes.fr/en/archives//inCompetition.html | archive-date=2013-11-10 | dead-url=yes }}</ref>，后来又参加2013年[[多伦多影展|多伦多影展]]<ref name="TIFF2013">{{cite web |url=http://www.guardian.co.uk/film/2013/jul/23/toronto-film-festival-lineup |title=Toronto film festival 2013: the full line-up |work=[[The_Guardian|The Guardian]] |location=London |accessdate=24 July 2013 |archive-date=2013-07-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130725010702/http://www.guardian.co.uk/film/2013/jul/23/toronto-film-festival-lineup |dead-url=no }}</ref> 与Reykjavik欧洲电影节。赢得第26届[[欧洲电影奖|欧洲电影奖]]最佳影片、导演、男演员和剪辑四个大奖<ref>{{cite web |url=http://ent.sina.com.cn/m/f/2013-12-09/10474057095.shtml |language= |title=《绝美之城》成“欧洲奥斯卡”大赢家 |publisher=天天新报 |date=2013年12月9日 |accessdate= |archive-date=2013-12-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131213211431/http://ent.sina.com.cn/m/f/2013-12-09/10474057095.shtml |dead-url=no }}</ref>，以及[[金球奖|金球奖]]、[[英国电影学院奖|英国电影学院奖]]和[[第86届奥斯卡金像奖|第86届奥斯卡]][[奥斯卡最佳外语片|最佳外语片]]<ref>[http://www.cna.com.tw/news/firstnews/201403030007-1.aspx 奧斯卡2014完整得獎名單] {{Wayback|url=http://www.cna.com.tw/news/firstnews/201403030007-1.aspx |date=20140306114358 }}，中央社，2014年3月3日</ref><ref name="Italy">{{cite web |url=http://variety.com/2013/film/news/italy-picks-sorrentinos-beauty-as-its-oscar-contender-1200666669/ |title=Italy Picks Sorrentino's ''Beauty'' As Its Oscar Contender |first=Nick |last=Vivarelli |work=[[Variety_(magazine)|Variety]] |publisher=[[PMC_(company)|Penske Media Corporation]] |date=25 September 2013 |accessdate=2 November 2013 |archive-date=2013-11-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131107083748/http://variety.com/2013/film/news/italy-picks-sorrentinos-beauty-as-its-oscar-contender-1200666669/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://ent.sina.com.cn/m/f/hlw/2014-03-03/10514105302.shtml |language= |title=详讯：《绝美之城》获奥斯卡最佳外语片 |publisher=新浪娱乐 |date=2014年3月3日 |accessdate= |archive-date=2014-03-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140309093209/http://ent.sina.com.cn/m/f/hlw/2014-03-03/10514105302.shtml |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

==剧情==
时年65岁的捷普是生长于[[罗马|罗马]]的作家，他经历过万众瞩目也经历过玩世不恭，经历过尔虞我诈，人生让他拥有一双冷静而透彻的眼睛，他直视罗马这座表面荣华但背后却遍布罪恶与堕落的“绝美-{}-之城”。

